Quality: FLAC + Cue + M3U8 + Log [Cover Front Back 4Cd + Inlay Box]

I could never have imagined that I would be so enthusiastic about these recordings. How, I wondered, could Rod Stewart's rather gravelly voice cope with these classic and rather sophisticated songs which I love but which present a challenge to many singers? How wrong can you be! I absolutely love all the numbers, and almost without exception the backing is superb. These songs really lift your spirits on a grey day and I have come to appreciate Rod Stewart's voice even more in these CDs than on the type of songs with which he is usually associated. Four wonderful CDs
